{"tid":2070651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疾控中心：沒證據新型肺炎經食品傳播 籲少接觸生食物","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:47.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2894509dbbf467c5e59e7e43fa5af9ad8e02bbf3","tid":2070651,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"疾控中心：沒證據新型肺炎經食品傳播 籲少接觸生食物<br />\n2020-06-19 HKT 17:04<br />\n<br />\n北京昨日再有25宗新型肺炎的確診個案，當中18人來自新發地市場所在的豐台區。<br />\n<br />\n海關總署衞生檢疫司副司長宋悅謙表示，在新發地市場出現群體感染個案後，已對來自疫情高風險國家或地區的水產品、肉類、冷凍蔬菜和水生動物等，開展病毒風險監測，截至昨日已檢取樣本超過1萬5千多個，包括貨物、包裝和環境樣本，全部結果屬陰性。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533014-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533014-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a873f65c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533014-20200619.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=63f2073d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533014-20200619.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家會否因近日三文魚感染事件而決定不吃生的食物?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"73ef796a4fd19d2af9804c83dbdd8b4c9e4b076e","tid":2070651,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"講真再咁樣銷毀食物法<br />\n根本就冇野俾班北京人食"}]}